The paper discusses efficient querying of Description Logic (DL) ontologies, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The paper also proposes a revised method for instance checking, which is a fundamental task in database systems (cs.DB) and DL reasoning (cs.DL). Finally, the paper discusses scalability and parallelization, which are important topics in software engineering (cs.SE).
